 "remarks": "Stunning Colonial in desirable Cranbury! - Updated kitchen with white cabinetry, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and subway tile backsplash! - Amazing family room with custom stone fireplace and lots of natural light! - French doors in family room open up to private deck with newer composite decking! - Light &amp; bright living room and dining room areas - Bedroom + office on main level - 2nd floor features stunning primary suite with vaulted ceiling in bedroom and en-suite bath + 2 large walk-in closets - 2 additional bedrooms on the 2nd floor - Large basement space is mostly finished for additional living area + unfinished storage space - Detached 2 car garage - Great back yard space offers lots of privacy! - Hardwood floors throughout! - Fresh paint, new stove, newer fridge, recessed lighting - Very convenient location, just minutes to shopping, dining, and beaches!",
